title: [Brazzers] Teens Like It Big - Jade Jantzen (Yoga Freaks ep: 3)
description:
On this very special episode of Yoga Freaks, Jade Jantzen enters the studio ready to give it her all. Yogi Master Xander blindfolds his young student to enhance her experience, and boy does it get enhanced. Jade is willing to do anything her teacher asks - even take it from two guys at once. Until next time, Namaste!
